response.original_title: ROH & NJPW War Of The Worlds 2017: New York City
response.overview: May 12th, 2017 :: Ring Of Honor and New Japan Pro Wrestling present the third night of the 2017 War Of The Worlds Tour live from New York City. Matches include:  • ROH World Title Three Way Match Christopher Daniels (c) vs. Jay Lethal vs. Cody Rhodes  • Hiroshi Tanahashi vs. Adam Cole  • ROH World Television Title Match The Young Bucks (Matt Jackson & Nick Jackson) (c) vs. Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI & Tetsuya Naito)  • ROH World Television Title Match Marty Scurll (c) vs. Matt Sydal  •ROH World Six Man Tag Team Title No Disqualification Match Bully Ray & The Briscoes (Jay Briscoe & Mark Briscoe) (c) vs. CHAOS (Beretta, Hirooki Goto & Rocky Romero)  • Will Ospreay vs. Jay White  • War Machine (Hanson & Ray Rowe) vs. Los Ingobernables de Japon (EVIL & SANADA) vs. Search And Destroy (Chris Sabin & Jonathan Gresham) (w/Alex Shelley)  • Frankie Kazarian vs. Hangman Page
